      • createNewHologram

        public Hologram createNewHologram(java.lang.String id,
                                  java.util.List<java.lang.String> lines,
                                  double lineSpread,
                                  org.bukkit.Location location)
        Allows you to create a packet hologram which you can customize based on the server's version.
        Parameters:
        lines - A list of the lines for the hologram to display (include color codes).
        lineSpread - How far apart should each line be from each other?
        location - The location where it should be displayed.
        Returns:
        The pre-built hologram object. Use the .create() method to create the packet before showing players.
